  <abstract>Supportive editorial from Wilford O. Cross to Chattanooga Times. Cross calls the investigation a "revival of McCarthyism." He also states that behind the investigation is a "crypto-fascist movement," also seeking to resist the Supreme Court's decision in Brown v. Board of Education, which include white councils and the Ku Klux Klan. He closes with a mention that this should frighten all who care about individual liberties, because if this investigation succeeds, all will be at stake.</abstract>
